data.description: Welcome to 15110 Field Sparrow, a stunning single-family home located in the desirable Redbird Ranch Community. This beautifully maintained property offers a comfortable and stylish living environment that surely will impress and it includes FULLY PAID OFF SOLAR PANELS that can save you thousands annually. This property also includes GE water softener, Nest thermostat, reverse osmosis system and irrigation system!    As you step inside, you'll be greeted by an inviting entryway, showcasing an open floor plan that is perfect for both entertaining and everyday living. The spacious living room features high ceilings, allowing for an abundance of natural light to flood the space, creating a warm and welcoming atmosphere.    This perfectly equipped kitchen with modern stainless steel appliances, granite counter tops, plenty of cabinet space, and a convenient center island for meal prep. Adjacent to the kitchen is a charming breakfast nook, providing the perfect spot for casual dining.    Step outside into the backyard oasis, where you will find a covered patio, ideal for hosting summer barbecues or simply enjoying a peaceful evening outdoors. The backyard is also generously sized and fully fenced, providing a safe and private space for children and pets to play.    Don't miss the opportunity to make 15110 Field Sparrow your forever home.
